<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1620] Need to use special StoreScanner constructor for major compactions (passed sf, no caching, etc)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1620</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Should not cache blocks during major compactions like with minor compactions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, need to only work on passed StoreFiles.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12429684">HBASE-1620</key>
            <summary>Need to use special StoreScanner constructor for major compactions (passed sf, no caching, etc)</summary>
